SUMMARY:Board of Directors Meeting
DESCRIPTION:The Energy Corridor District® Board of Directors meet every second Friday of the month at 8:30 a.m. Meetings are held at: Energy Corridor District 777 North Eldridge Parkway\, Suite 270\, Houston\, Texas 77079 Board of Directors Meeting dates/times are subject to change. Call 281-759-3800 to confirm meeting schedules. \nView Meeting Documents here.
