SUMMARY:Unified Topgolf Pro-Am (Houston-Katy)
DESCRIPTION:The Unified Topgolf Pro-Am is one of the most exciting and meaningful community partnership events hosted by Special Olympics Texas\, bringing together athletes\, families\, coaches\, volunteers\, corporate partners\, and local business leaders for an unforgettable day of golf\, laughter\, connection\, and community impact. \nEach bay includes a Special Olympics Texas athlete paired alongside five golfers\, creating a truly unique experience where relationships\, memories\, and meaningful moments are built throughout the day. From friendly competition and team spirit to incredible conversations and shared experiences\, the event is designed to bring people together in a fun and welcoming environment while directly supporting local athletes and programs. \nProceeds from the Unified Topgolf Pro-Am help provide year-round sports training\, competitions\, health initiatives\, leadership development\, and educational opportunities for children\, teenagers\, and adults with intellectual disabilities throughout the greater Houston area. As the event continues growing each year\, the Unified Topgolf Pro-Am has quickly become a tremendous opportunity for organizations and community members to make a real impact while being part of something incredibly energetic\, uplifting\, and memorable. \nFor more information regarding sponsorship opportunities\, team entries\, volunteer involvement\, or sponsorship opportunities\, please reach out to Jared Kossover\, Strategic Partnerships Manager with Special Olympics Texas \nJared Kossover \nE: jkossover@sotx.org \nC: 737-867-9659
URL:https://energycorridor.org/event/unified-topgolf-pro-am-houston-katy/2026-09-18/2/
LOCATION:Topgolf-Katy\, 1030 Memorial Brook Blvd\, Houston\, TX 77084\, Houston\, 77084
CATEGORIES:Community Events
ORGANIZER;CN="Special Olympics Texas":MAILTO:jkossover@sotx.org
END:VEVENT
